Five boys aged 13 and 14 will appear in youth court charged with the rape of a 12-year-old girl. 

The teenagers are charged with raping and sexually assaulting a child under 13 after two alleged incidents in Rastrick, West Yorkshire. 

It is thought the children are all known to one another.  

